    "en": {
      "title": "Motorcycle gunmen kill two men in Ambalangoda; Police say murders likely linked to Tuesday\u2019s (26) shooting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Two people were gunned donw by an unknown gunan on a motorbike in the Galagoda area in Ambalangoda.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said one person died on the spot, and the other died upon admission to the Balapitiya Hospital.",
        "The deceased were identified as a 49-year-old man and a 44-year-old man from Galagoda.",
        "Police suspect that this shooting may be linked to the shooting in Urawatte, Ambalangoda yesterday (26) that killed one man.",
        "Motorcycle gunmen kill two men in Ambalangoda; Police say murders likely linked to Tuesday\u2019s (26) shooting",
        "Chinese Ambassador meets Ali Sabry to discuss current situation in Sri Lanka",
        "IMF says Sri Lanka needs to talk with China about debt restructuring",
        "US \u2013 SL relations can flourish in a Sri Lanka that respects Human Rights \u2013 US Ambassador",
        "Attack on Journalists: MTV Network Gives Evidence to Human Rights Commission"
